description: Cityrea Sverige - A Swedish Phone App
overview: Cityrea a Swedish Company that gives out free reciepts to it’s visitors for cheaper products or services. Cityrea was founded in the town called Uppsala in the year 2012 and is growing more popularity with time with more satisfied visitors for each day. Cityrea’s mission is to make people get more for less money with latest updated list on new reciepts that the Visitors can take in advantage. If you live in Sweden and are looking for cheaper solutions don’t hesitate to download the app right now and today. Cityrea App is supported both for iPhone and Android.
